  "body": "When the vsphere volume is mounted, it fails to set the ownership to the fsGroup.\n\nRight before the end of the SetUpAt method at https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/pkg/volume/vsphere_volume/vsphere_volume.go#L231 the volume should have it's ownership changed by running \n`if !b.readOnly {\n        volume.SetVolumeOwnership(b, fsGroup)\n    }`\n",
